Ah! That explains why you can’t download it — the sandbox here doesn’t always allow direct file download links for Postman JSON files. No worries, I can give you the **full Postman collection JSON content** directly. You can then **copy it into a `.json` file locally** and import it into Postman.

Here’s the full Postman collection content:

```json
{
